entry.summary:
The data set consists of (U-Th)/He ages collected from three vertical profiles
      from the the Kukri Hills (north side of the Ferrar Glacier) of Southern
      Victoria Land.  The data set provides information on the cooling history and
      hence the denduation history of the Transantarctic Mountains in this area.
      Analyses were all carried out at the (U-Th)/He lab of Ken Farley at the
      Californai Institute of Technology.
entry.dataset_id: (U-Th)/He ages from the Kukri Hills of southern Victoria Land
entry.title: (U-Th)/He ages from the Kukri Hills of southern Victoria Land
